ndgain-nd-readiness-governance.def: The stability of the society and institutional arrangements that contribute to the investment risks. A stable country with high governance capacity reassures investors that the invested capitals could grow under the help of responsive public services and without significant interruption. This is measure by the indicators: Political stability and non-violence, Control of corruption, Rule of law, and Regulatory quality.
ndgain-nd-readiness-governance.name: Governance Readiness
